Package model.traffic

Class Summary
Block This class represents a blockage, in a location, that creates detours and slows affected segments
Coord A class to represent coordinates
CoordStr A String Version of the Coordinate, it is used mainly in all calls that do not require any coordinate math and instead are printed somewhere.
Entry Helper class for event log Records an event as a time and and Event
Event Events that occur during the running of the simulator A generic Event Log used to pass information or store events
EventLog The Eventlog is a generic class to store and address sets of related events or logable output
EventLogTest used to test EventLog, not necessary in any other class.
Options Class to store Options of the Simulator
Point Deprecated.  
Route The route class represents an expected route, it is basically an array of segments and methods to support it as a Route
Segment The segment class represents a line between two coordinates, or a segment in a route defined by a set of coordinates.
Trace The trace class represents the actual route taken as polled at each interval in the form of a set Coordinates
